title: 75: Worst Fake ID Stories
itunes:title: Worst Fake ID Stories
description:
The team dives in to the world of bad fake ID's, why Hooters is so depressing, and how Michael got scammed in NYC. They also discuss how a listener ate his sibling's pet goldfish. This is a podcast about making documentaries.
